class.description:
@brief ActuatorControl plugin
@plugin mavros/actuator_control

Sends actuator controls to FCU controller.

@brief Command plugin.
@plugin mavros/command

Send any command via COMMAND_LONG

@brief Global position plugin.
@plugin mavros/global_position

Publishes global position. Conversion from GPS LLA to ECEF allows
publishing local position to TF and PoseWithCovarianceStamped.

@brief home position plugin.
@plugin mavros/home_position

Publishes home position.

@brief Local position plugin.
@plugin mavros/local_position

Publish local position to TF, PositionStamped, TwistStamped
and Odometry

@brief nav controller output plugin.
@plugin mavros/nav_controller_output

Publishes nav_controller_output message https://mavlink.io/en/messages/common.html#NAV_CONTROLLER_OUTPUT

@brief Setpoint acceleration/force plugin
@plugin mavros/setpoint_accel

Send setpoint accelerations/forces to FCU controller.

@brief Setpoint attitude plugin
@plugin mavros/setpoint_attitude

Send setpoint attitude/orientation/thrust to FCU controller.

@brief Setpoint position plugin
@plugin mavros/setpoint_position

Send setpoint positions to FCU controller.

@brief Setpoint RAW plugin
@plugin mavros/setpoint_raw

Send position setpoints and publish current state (return loop).
User can decide what set of filed needed for operation via IGNORE bits.

@brief Setpoint TRAJECTORY plugin
@plugin mavros/setpoint_trajectory

Receive trajectory setpoints and send setpoint_raw setpoints along the trajectory.

@brief Setpoint velocity plugin
@plugin mavros/setpoint_velocity

Send setpoint velocities to FCU controller.

@brief System status plugin.
@plugin mavros/sys_status

Required by all plugins.
